<view class="page">
  <view class="nav">
    <view class="back" bindtap="onBack">‹</view>
    <text>中医问询</text>
  </view>

  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-copy">
      <text class="hero-kicker">AI 健康助手</text>
      <text class="hero-title">把症状说清楚</text>
      <text class="hero-desc">结合体质、健康数据与中医调养知识，生成更适合日常参考的建议。</text>
      <button class="hero-btn" bindtap="goResult">开始问询</button>
    </view>
    <image class="hero-art" src="../../assets/images/ai-consult-hero-lite.jpg" mode="aspectFill" />
  </view>

  <view class="intro-card">
    <view class="section-title compact">
      <view></view>
      <text>测评介绍</text>
    </view>
    <text class="intro-text">可输入当前不适，也可以选择下方常见症状。系统会根据问询内容，辅助整理健康状态与调养方向。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="panel symptom-panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>症状</text>
    </view>
    <view class="input-row">
      <text class="placeholder">输入症状或选择下方标签</text>
      <button>添加</button>
    </view>
    <view class="tag-list">
      <text class="tag {{index === 0 ? 'active' : ''}}" wx:for="{{tags}}" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>常见问询</text>
    </view>
    <view class="quick-list">
      <view class="quick-row" wx:for="{{quickQuestions}}" wx:key="title">
        <image src="{{item.icon}}" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view class="quick-copy">
          <text class="quick-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="quick-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="quick-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="start-btn" bindtap="goResult">AI 问询</button>

  <view class="panel last-panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>问询记录</text>
    </view>
    <view class="history-list">
      <view class="history-row" wx:for="{{history}}" wx:key="title">
        <image src="../../assets/images/icon-ai-chat.png" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view>
          <text class="history-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="history-time">{{item.time}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="history-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
